generalizations about them.

00:48:57.140 --> 00:49:07.060
In 1573, Philip
II, understanding

00:49:07.060 --> 00:49:13.840
the military, religious, and
financial availability of land

00:49:13.840 --> 00:49:18.790
in the hinterland
of the Americas,

00:49:18.790 --> 00:49:23.740
created an argument or set
of principles on which towns

00:49:23.740 --> 00:49:25.210
would be laid out.

00:49:25.210 --> 00:49:29.005
These are called in English
the Laws of the Indies.

00:49:32.220 --> 00:49:47.650
They describe the way you are
set of rules which specify--

00:49:51.480 --> 00:50:00.145
I'd better hurry-- the size
of the individual components

00:50:00.145 --> 00:50:00.645
of the town.

00:50:03.750 --> 00:50:05.460
The main plaza
was to be oriented

00:50:05.460 --> 00:50:08.040
so its four corners
pointed to the four

00:50:08.040 --> 00:50:10.245
cardinal points of a compass.

00:50:10.245 --> 00:50:14.490
It shall not be smaller
than 200 feet wide

00:50:14.490 --> 00:50:19.680
and 300 feet long, no larger
than 800 feet long, and so on.

00:50:23.730 --> 00:50:27.900
It had a formal
message to convey

00:50:27.900 --> 00:50:32.850
to the Indians who located
around where the new settlement

00:50:32.850 --> 00:50:35.910
tool place.

00:50:35.910 --> 00:50:39.060
"When the Indians see them, they
will be filled with wonder."

00:50:39.060 --> 00:50:42.510
That is the church.

00:50:42.510 --> 00:50:46.620
The Indians should not
be let into this town

00:50:46.620 --> 00:50:49.230
until the church is finished.

00:50:49.230 --> 00:50:53.820
The church architecture
represents the formal attribute

00:50:53.820 --> 00:50:56.000
of colonial superiority.

00:50:58.580 --> 00:51:01.430
The Indians must understand
that they have been conquered

00:51:01.430 --> 00:51:05.750
by a superior race,
therefore the church,

00:51:05.750 --> 00:51:10.040
which is to the
Spanish the highest

00:51:10.040 --> 00:51:15.950
form of contact with God and
the only formal attribute

00:51:15.950 --> 00:51:20.510
that we have other than
behavior and ritual,

00:51:20.510 --> 00:51:26.670
becomes the temple of
the Roman town, at least

00:51:26.670 --> 00:51:28.175
to the Laws of the Indies town.

00:51:38.180 --> 00:51:44.180
St. Augustine, Florida
was the first application

00:51:44.180 --> 00:51:48.540
of the Laws of the
Indies in 1565.

00:51:48.540 --> 00:51:55.550
Los Angeles was the last of
the Spanish settlements, 1781.

00:51:55.550 --> 00:52:00.770
So the period of
this 1565 to 1781

00:52:00.770 --> 00:52:07.040
takes care of many of
the towns, St. Augustine.

00:52:07.040 --> 00:52:11.240
The Anglo-American grid, which
is the grid of experience

00:52:11.240 --> 00:52:18.140
to the North, overlaps with
the Laws of the Indies grid

00:52:18.140 --> 00:52:20.570
