00:53:10.440 --> 00:53:13.860
Sao Paulo, which is now one
of the world's largest cities,

00:53:13.860 --> 00:53:17.040
one of the few 20
million-person cities,

00:53:17.040 --> 00:53:20.010
has its origin in
nothing more than three

00:53:20.010 --> 00:53:25.860
