00:56:39.610 --> 00:56:45.250
Essentially the components
of the grid of expediency

00:56:45.250 --> 00:56:46.650
are the following--

00:56:46.650 --> 00:56:50.250
number 1, the Land
Ordinance of 1785

00:56:50.250 --> 00:56:55.320
which divided the unbuilt
parts of the United States,

00:56:55.320 --> 00:56:58.570
first only part of
it, then finally

00:56:58.570 --> 00:57:04.410
most of the United States,
into a grid of 6 by 6 miles.

00:57:04.410 --> 00:57:08.070
Local authorities or
local towns could then

00:57:08.070 --> 00:57:10.890
subdivide within this grid.

00:57:10.890 --> 00:57:17.400
Most of the subdivision was
taken care of by two forces,

00:57:17.400 --> 00:57:21.630
either private development,
which subdivided length

00:57:21.630 --> 00:57:30.600
into smaller units, or the
railroad companies which

00:57:30.600 --> 00:57:34.260
merged [INAUDIBLE] develop
[INAUDIBLE] profits

00:57:34.260 --> 00:57:36.420
hand-in-hand.

00:57:36.420 --> 00:57:40.050
The standard plan used
by railroads for 33 towns

00:57:40.050 --> 00:57:44.400
developed by one group
alone in Illinois.

00:57:44.400 --> 00:57:46.440
There was another
force at work, and that

00:57:46.440 --> 00:57:51.240
was the movement of religious
groups such as the Mormons

00:57:51.240 --> 00:57:53.190
across this country.

00:57:53.190 --> 00:57:57.930
There were Mormons starting
in 1913 up in New York.

00:57:57.930 --> 00:58:02.690
They moved to a Kirkland, Ohio,
they were pushed out of there.

00:58:02.690 --> 00:58:05.970
They move to Missouri,
the revelation

00:58:05.970 --> 00:58:08.430
that this is the new place.

00:58:08.430 --> 00:58:10.350
They moved out of there.

00:58:10.350 --> 00:58:15.900
They went to Nauvoo in Illinois
and spent the winter quarters

00:58:15.900 --> 00:58:18.630
in 1847 in Nebraska.

00:58:18.630 --> 00:58:24.450
And finally in 1847, after
a journey of 17 years,

00:58:24.450 --> 00:58:27.900
Brigham Young said,
this is the place

00:58:27.900 --> 00:58:31.350
and he developed Salt Lake City.

00:58:31.350 --> 00:58:37.500
Salt Lake City is a grid city,
which has a set of micro-rules

00:58:37.500 --> 00:58:38.880
about street--

00:58:38.880 --> 00:58:42.660
which lots can be facing
the streets, and so on.

00:58:42.660 --> 00:58:46.215
I'll talk about that later.

00:58:51.280 --> 00:58:59.440
Two people who've argued
about the grid of expediency--

00:58:59.440 --> 00:59:02.650
Lewis Mumford has
called urban land

00:59:02.650 --> 00:59:07.180
becoming a mere commodity
by the parceling of land

00:59:07.180 --> 00:59:11.090
a quick conversion of
farmstead into real estate

00:59:11.090 --> 00:59:14.050
and a quick sale.

00:59:14.050 --> 00:59:18.920
Richard Sennett has written
in the Conscience of the Eye

00:59:18.920 --> 00:59:22.570
about the Protestant
ethic of being

00:59:22.570 --> 00:59:28.690
satisfied with what he calls
the Protestant ethic of space.

00:59:28.690 --> 00:59:31.690
"Here is where the
good found its place.

00:59:31.690 --> 00:59:34.570
It was a space for
economic competition

00:59:34.570 --> 00:59:36.910
to be played upon
like a chessboard.

00:59:36.910 --> 00:59:40.540
It was a space of neutrality,
and neutrality achieved

00:59:40.540 --> 00:59:45.780
by denying to the environment
any value of its own."

00:59:45.780 --> 00:59:52.210
This attempt to
argue in this way

00:59:52.210 --> 00:59:58.030
argues that, if I
buy any IBM share,

00:59:58.030 --> 01:00:00.160
I buy a piece of
its typewriters--

01:00:00.160 --> 01:00:02.590
I don't know if they
still makes them--

01:00:02.590 --> 01:00:06.820
a piece of real estate,
a piece of its land.

01:00:06.820 --> 01:00:13.210
My $5 share, or $47
share, is a commodity

01:00:13.210 --> 01:00:17.080
as a reduction of a
large complex whole.

01:00:17.080 --> 01:00:20.620
The argument is that the
city is a complex whole.

01:00:20.620 --> 01:00:24.790
And reducing it to a
commodity by gridding it

01:00:24.790 --> 01:00:29.870
takes no account of the
essential qualities of a city.

01:00:29.870 --> 01:00:35.410
There's a kind of cosmic memory
associated with his critique.

01:00:38.170 --> 01:00:42.370
How capitalism developed
Boston with no grid

01:00:42.370 --> 01:00:45.060
is, of course, a question
I would ask Richard Sennett

01:00:45.060 --> 01:00:46.120
or Lewis Mumford.

01:00:48.870 --> 01:00:52.200
Not all American cities
were like Chicago.

01:00:58.140 --> 01:01:03.660
The cattaneo of cities
on the East Coast,

01:01:03.660 --> 01:01:05.520
I have got time to--

01:01:05.520 --> 01:01:07.710
but they essentially
are best described

01:01:07.710 --> 01:01:13.050
by the Plan of Savannah, written
very elegantly in an analysis

01:01:13.050 --> 01:01:16.590
by Stanford Anderson, who's
a Professor in the Department

01:01:16.590 --> 01:01:18.030
of Architecture.

01:01:18.030 --> 01:01:21.060
It essentially
takes the grid plan

01:01:21.060 --> 01:01:26.220
and centers it
into neighborhoods

01:01:26.220 --> 01:01:28.350
with parks in the center.

01:01:28.350 --> 01:01:32.460
It divides the road
system into wider roads

01:01:32.460 --> 01:01:34.500
which run north-south.

01:01:34.500 --> 01:01:39.180
Why do the roads in Manhattan
are wider, 100 feet wide,

01:01:39.180 --> 01:01:43.170
going north-south, and 50
feet wide going east-west?

01:01:47.510 --> 01:01:50.540
What are the roads
connecting in the Rome sense?

01:01:53.720 --> 01:02:00.180
Docks, water traffic on
either side of the island.

01:02:00.180 --> 01:02:03.200
So the east-west street
should have been wider

01:02:03.200 --> 01:02:05.590
than the north-south street.

01:02:05.590 --> 01:02:09.225
The north-south are avenues.

01:02:09.225 --> 01:02:09.725
Why?

01:02:12.290 --> 01:02:14.540
Let's try to answer
that question

01:02:14.540 --> 01:02:19.640
in talking about the 1811 Plan.

01:02:19.640 --> 01:02:24.590
The 1811 Plan was
no cosmic plan.

01:02:24.590 --> 01:02:27.260
According to Roy
Strickland's writing,

01:02:27.260 --> 01:02:29.720
it simply adapted
the measurements

01:02:29.720 --> 01:02:34.310
of the British
settlement, which took

01:02:34.310 --> 01:02:42.630
over the Dutch original
1623 settlement.

01:02:42.630 --> 01:02:46.590
There was a wonderful exhibition
of the 1811 Plan in New York

01:02:46.590 --> 01:02:47.770
last year.

01:02:47.770 --> 01:02:49.950
I don't know if
any of you saw it.

01:02:49.950 --> 01:02:52.200
Did you see it?

01:02:52.200 --> 01:02:54.260
Pretty.

01:02:54.260 --> 01:02:58.430
It says more than
I can possibly say.

01:02:58.430 --> 01:03:04.280
In the commissioner's
report, it says,

01:03:04.280 --> 01:03:06.665
"we could not bear in
mind that a city is

01:03:06.665 --> 01:03:10.370
to compose principally of
the habitations of men,

01:03:10.370 --> 01:03:13.610
and that straight-sided
and right-angled houses

01:03:13.610 --> 01:03:18.960
are the most cheap to build and
the most convenient to live in,

01:03:18.960 --> 01:03:23.480
effective these plain and simple
reflections are decisive."

01:03:26.700 --> 01:03:36.400
So here we have a plan which
many people have commented on,

01:03:36.400 --> 01:03:42.766
a plan which is allowed enormous
subdivisional specialization,

01:03:42.766 --> 01:03:46.720
a plan which has allowed
the southern sector to grow

01:03:46.720 --> 01:03:48.730
as a financial center.

01:03:48.730 --> 01:03:55.910
A central part is a part
for department stores,

01:03:55.910 --> 01:03:59.710
the combination of
housing and offices

01:03:59.710 --> 01:04:05.275
and commerce in the
rest of the plan.

01:04:08.350 --> 01:04:13.450
Essentially, it's a plan which
[INAUDIBLE] has correctly

01:04:13.450 --> 01:04:18.370
written about as delirious.

01:04:18.370 --> 01:04:23.920
One of the advantages
of a free system.

01:04:23.920 --> 01:04:28.030
There have been rules about
building a Manhattan ever

01:04:28.030 --> 01:04:31.771
since, the protection
of the sidewalks--

01:04:31.771 --> 01:04:33.700
the height at
which buildings get

01:04:33.700 --> 01:04:36.430
build, and so on, over time.

01:04:36.430 --> 01:04:40.180
But the central
grid has remained.

01:04:40.180 --> 01:04:44.290
It is fundamental to the
grid system of New York

01:04:44.290 --> 01:04:47.335
that Central Park
connects east and west.

01:04:50.420 --> 01:04:53.990
The grid system is the
fundamental flexibility

01:04:53.990 --> 01:04:57.150
phenomenon of Manhattan.

01:04:57.150 --> 01:05:00.530
